annotationA: CG9281, isoform B; ATPase activity, coupled to transmembrane movement of substances; ATP binding; transporter activity
annotationB: Elongation factor 1-gamma; Ef1gamma associates with other EF1 subunits (alpha/beta/delta). It binds tubulin and Doa protein kinase, which in turns phosphorylates Ef1gamma. Ef1gamma regulates organelle movement along microtubules
